  "title": "三个理由说明为何 Anthropic 的 Claude Mythos 发布被过度炒作了",
  "url": "https://garymarcus.substack.com/p/three-reasons-to-think-that-the-claude",
  "date": "2026-04-09 19:15:13",
  "author": "Gary Marcus",
  "siteName": "Marcus on AI",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div dir=\"auto\" class=\"body markup\">\n   <p>Three reasons to think that yesterday’s Mythos announcement from Anthropic was overblown:</p>\n   <ol>\n    <li>\n     <p>Where Tom Fridman worried in his Times column yesterday about kids accidentally blowing up the power grid…</p>\n     <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n      <figure>\n       <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!NhiT!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04de9b4b-483a-477e-adc6-852e1739bb5e_1268x293.jpeg\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel=\"\" class=\"image-link image2 can-restack\"> \n        <div class=\"image2-inset can-restack\">\n         <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/aeec49fe-241d-4275-be0a-78b333c3e400/public 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260409200444_04de9b4b-483a-477e-adc6-852e1739bb5e_1268x293.jpeg 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260409200444_04de9b4b-483a-477e-adc6-852e1739bb5e_1268x293.jpeg 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/10f93fe1-1735-4061-6c76-e64523f22100/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260409200444_04de9b4b-483a-477e-adc6-852e1739bb5e_1268x293.jpeg\" width=\"1268\" height=\"293\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/04de9b4b-483a-477e-adc6-852e1739bb5e_1268x293.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:293,&quot;width&quot;:1268,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:68338,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://garymarcus.substack.com/i/193721695?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04de9b4b-483a-477e-adc6-852e1739bb5e_1268x293.jpeg&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6188ca1c-32fd-4920-f83b-7454d4c8b400/public 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260409200444_04de9b4b-483a-477e-adc6-852e1739bb5e_1268x293.jpeg 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260409200444_04de9b4b-483a-477e-adc6-852e1739bb5e_1268x293.jpeg 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260409200444_04de9b4b-483a-477e-adc6-852e1739bb5e_1268x293.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" fetchpriority=\"high\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n        </div> \n       </a>\n      </figure>\n     </div>\n     <p><span>… the actual system tested was given a </span><em>much</em><span> easier job than in real life, with “sandboxing” turned off, making it more of proof of concept than an immediate threat.</span></p>\n     <a href=\"https://x.com/philogroves/status/2042195139477557499?s=61\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-component-name=\"Twitter2ToDOM\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset\"> \n      <div data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://x.com/philogroves/status/2042195139477557499?s=61&quot;,&quot;full_text&quot;:&quot;Mythos' Firefox exploitation didn't actually have sandbox enabled and built on top of research from Opus. Shocker. &quot;,&quot;username&quot;:&quot;PhiloGroves&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Philo Groves&quot;,&quot;profile_image_url&quot;:&quot;https://pbs.substack.com/profile_images/2020890550929408000/A4AmLyKm_normal.jpg&quot;,&quot;date&quot;:&quot;2026-04-09T10:57:18.000Z&quot;,&quot;photos&quot;:[{&quot;img_url&quot;:&quot;https://pbs.substack.com/media/HFdVfKcXsAAu_Xp.jpg&quot;,&quot;link_url&quot;:&quot;https://t.co/xwWUsb82hW&quot;}],&quot;quoted_tweet&quot;:{},&quot;reply_count&quot;:11,&quot;retweet_count&quot;:55,&quot;like_count&quot;:651,&quot;impression_count&quot;:83416,&quot;expanded_url&quot;:null,&quot;video_url&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false}\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-12 pc-padding-16 pc-reset bg-primary-zk6FDl outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-md sizing-border-box-DggLA4 pressable-lg-kV7yq8 font-text-qe4AeH tweet-fWkQfo twitter-embed\">\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-row pc-gap-12 pc-alignItems-center pc-reset\">\n        <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n         <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" title=\"User\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n          <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260409200444_A4AmLyKm.jpg 40w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/75b2589c-cb1c-445f-b990-dbcd6ec73800/public 80w, https://image.jido.dev/20260409200444_A4AmLyKm.jpg 120w\" sizes=\"40px\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260409200444_A4AmLyKm.jpg\" sizes=\"40px\" alt=\"X avatar for @PhiloGroves\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260409200444_A4AmLyKm.jpg 40w, https://image.jido.dev/20260409200444_A4AmLyKm.jpg 80w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/44559071-6fb5-4271-c778-1bf051f08800/public 120w\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" draggable=\"false\" class=\"img-OACg1c object-fit-cover-u4ReeV pencraft pc-reset\"></picture>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-reset flex-grow-rzmknG\">\n         <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset weight-semibold-uqA4FV reset-IxiVJZ\">Philo Groves</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s reset-IxiVJZ\">@PhiloGroves</span>\n        </div>\n        <svg role=\"img\" style=\"height:20px;width:20px;\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke=\"#000\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n         <g>\n          <title></title><path stroke=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M13.2879 19.1666L8.66337 12.575L2.87405 19.1666H0.424805L7.57674 11.0258L0.424805 0.833252H6.71309L11.0717 7.04577L16.5327 0.833252H18.982L12.1619 8.59699L19.5762 19.1666H13.2879ZM16.0154 17.3083H14.3665L3.93176 2.69159H5.58092L9.7601 8.54422L10.4828 9.55981L16.0154 17.3083Z\"></path>\n         </g>\n        </svg>\n       </div>\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-15-Psle70 weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ text-aFN1BV\">Mythos' Firefox exploitation didn't actually have sandbox enabled and built on top of research from Opus. Shocker.</div>\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset bg-black-dCpgGg outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-sm overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 container-aGHQ9p\">\n        <img src=\"https://pbs.substack.com/media/HFdVfKcXsAAu_Xp.jpg\" class=\"image-c_FmAR\">\n       </div>\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n         <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">10:57 AM · Apr 9, 2026</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">83.4K Views</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n         <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">11 Replies</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">55 Reposts</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">651 Likes</span>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p><a href=\"https://aisle.com/blog/ai-cybersecurity-after-mythos-the-jagged-frontier\" rel=\"\">Open-weight models can already do a fair amount of what Mythos can do, in a simplified preparation</a><span>. Mythos is more sophisticated but perhaps not head-and-shoulders the way it was portrayed. </span></p>\n     <a href=\"https://x.com/clementdelangue/status/2041953761069793557?s=61\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-component-name=\"Twitter2ToDOM\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset\"> \n      <div data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://x.com/clementdelangue/status/2041953761069793557?s=61&quot;,&quot;full_text&quot;:&quot;\\&quot;But here is what we found when we tested: We took the specific vulnerabilities Anthropic showcases in their announcement, isolated the relevant code, and ran them through small, cheap, open-weights models. Those models recovered much of the same analysis. Eight out of eight&quot;,&quot;username&quot;:&quot;ClementDelangue&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;clem 🤗&quot;,&quot;profile_image_url&quot;:&quot;https://pbs.substack.com/profile_images/1100512198139498497/utHSJ4st_normal.png&quot;,&quot;date&quot;:&quot;2026-04-08T18:58:08.000Z&quot;,&quot;photos&quot;:[],&quot;quoted_tweet&quot;:{},&quot;reply_count&quot;:70,&quot;retweet_count&quot;:233,&quot;like_count&quot;:1527,&quot;impression_count&quot;:323023,&quot;expanded_url&quot;:null,&quot;video_url&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false}\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-12 pc-padding-16 pc-reset bg-primary-zk6FDl outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-md sizing-border-box-DggLA4 pressable-lg-kV7yq8 font-text-qe4AeH tweet-fWkQfo twitter-embed\">\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-row pc-gap-12 pc-alignItems-center pc-reset\">\n        <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n         <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" title=\"User\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n          <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260409200444_utHSJ4st.png 40w, https://image.jido.dev/20260409200445_utHSJ4st.png 80w, https://image.jido.dev/20260409200444_utHSJ4st.png 120w\" sizes=\"40px\"><img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/985596ea-7a5c-42e4-3146-e1eac2149d00/public\" sizes=\"40px\" alt=\"X avatar for @ClementDelangue\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/985596ea-7a5c-42e4-3146-e1eac2149d00/public 40w, https://image.jido.dev/20260409200444_utHSJ4st.png 80w, https://image.jido.dev/20260409200444_utHSJ4st.png 120w\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" draggable=\"false\" class=\"img-OACg1c object-fit-cover-u4ReeV pencraft pc-reset\"></picture>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-reset flex-grow-rzmknG\">\n         <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset weight-semibold-uqA4FV reset-IxiVJZ\">clem 🤗</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s reset-IxiVJZ\">@ClementDelangue</span>\n        </div>\n        <svg role=\"img\" style=\"height:20px;width:20px;\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke=\"#000\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n         <g>\n          <title></title><path stroke=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M13.2879 19.1666L8.66337 12.575L2.87405 19.1666H0.424805L7.57674 11.0258L0.424805 0.833252H6.71309L11.0717 7.04577L16.5327 0.833252H18.982L12.1619 8.59699L19.5762 19.1666H13.2879ZM16.0154 17.3083H14.3665L3.93176 2.69159H5.58092L9.7601 8.54422L10.4828 9.55981L16.0154 17.3083Z\"></path>\n         </g>\n        </svg>\n       </div>\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-15-Psle70 weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ text-aFN1BV\">\"But here is what we found when we tested: We took the specific vulnerabilities Anthropic showcases in their announcement, isolated the relevant code, and ran them through small, cheap, open-weights models. Those models recovered much of the same analysis. Eight out of eight</div>\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n         <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">6:58 PM · Apr 8, 2026</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">323K Views</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n         <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">70 Replies</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">233 Reposts</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">1.53K Likes</span>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>The model itself is incrementally better than previous recent models, but certainly not an off-the-chart breakthrough:</p>\n     <a href=\"https://x.com/ramez/status/2041946766598402459?s=61\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-component-name=\"Twitter2ToDOM\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset\"> \n      <div data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://x.com/ramez/status/2041946766598402459?s=61&quot;,&quot;full_text&quot;:&quot;Anthropic's Mythos does not appear to show any acceleration of ECI. After normalizing Anthropic's internal ECI with &lt;span class=\\&quot;tweet-fake-link\\&quot;&gt;@EpochAIResearch&lt;/span&gt; 's public ECI, it's clear that the two metrics are extremely close, and that Mythos is pretty much on trend, just slightly above GPT 5.4.  /1 &quot;,&quot;username&quot;:&quot;ramez&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Ramez Naam&quot;,&quot;profile_image_url&quot;:&quot;https://pbs.substack.com/profile_images/1897785621802061824/N9bBY8w6_normal.jpg&quot;,&quot;date&quot;:&quot;2026-04-08T18:30:21.000Z&quot;,&quot;photos&quot;:[{&quot;img_url&quot;:&quot;https://pbs.substack.com/media/HFZyuPDa8AEKJ2x.jpg&quot;,&quot;link_url&quot;:&quot;https://t.co/kZXk5L4XpG&quot;}],&quot;quoted_tweet&quot;:{},&quot;reply_count&quot;:28,&quot;retweet_count&quot;:65,&quot;like_count&quot;:578,&quot;impression_count&quot;:131566,&quot;expanded_url&quot;:null,&quot;video_url&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false}\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-12 pc-padding-16 pc-reset bg-primary-zk6FDl outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-md sizing-border-box-DggLA4 pressable-lg-kV7yq8 font-text-qe4AeH tweet-fWkQfo twitter-embed\">\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-row pc-gap-12 pc-alignItems-center pc-reset\">\n        <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n         <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" title=\"User\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n          <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3b173fd2-40f1-4ccd-7d22-7c1f2184fd00/public 40w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1a87e8a2-8806-4362-2d90-b5d8f1eada00/public 80w, https://image.jido.dev/20260409200444_N9bBY8w6.jpg 120w\" sizes=\"40px\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260409200444_N9bBY8w6.jpg\" sizes=\"40px\" alt=\"X avatar for @ramez\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260409200444_N9bBY8w6.jpg 40w, https://image.jido.dev/20260409200444_N9bBY8w6.jpg 80w, https://image.jido.dev/20260409200444_N9bBY8w6.jpg 120w\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" draggable=\"false\" class=\"img-OACg1c object-fit-cover-u4ReeV pencraft pc-reset\"></picture>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-reset flex-grow-rzmknG\">\n         <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset weight-semibold-uqA4FV reset-IxiVJZ\">Ramez Naam</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s reset-IxiVJZ\">@ramez</span>\n        </div>\n        <svg role=\"img\" style=\"height:20px;width:20px;\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke=\"#000\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n         <g>\n          <title></title><path stroke=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M13.2879 19.1666L8.66337 12.575L2.87405 19.1666H0.424805L7.57674 11.0258L0.424805 0.833252H6.71309L11.0717 7.04577L16.5327 0.833252H18.982L12.1619 8.59699L19.5762 19.1666H13.2879ZM16.0154 17.3083H14.3665L3.93176 2.69159H5.58092L9.7601 8.54422L10.4828 9.55981L16.0154 17.3083Z\"></path>\n         </g>\n        </svg>\n       </div>\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-15-Psle70 weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ text-aFN1BV\">\n        Anthropic's Mythos does not appear to show any acceleration of ECI. After normalizing Anthropic's internal ECI with <span class=\"tweet-fake-link\">@EpochAIResearch</span> 's public ECI, it's clear that the two metrics are extremely close, and that Mythos is pretty much on trend, just slightly above GPT 5.4. /1\n       </div>\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset bg-black-dCpgGg outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-sm overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 container-aGHQ9p\">\n        <img src=\"https://pbs.substack.com/media/HFZyuPDa8AEKJ2x.jpg\" class=\"image-c_FmAR\">\n       </div>\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n         <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">6:30 PM · Apr 8, 2026</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">132K Views</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n         <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">28 Replies</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">65 Reposts</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">578 Likes</span>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <p>To a certain degree, I feel that we were played. The demo was definitely proof of concept that we need to get our regulatory and technical house in order, but not the immediate threat the media and public was lead to believe.</p>\n   <div data-component-name=\"SubscribeWidget\" class=\"subscribe-widget\">\n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-justifyContent-center pc-reset\">\n     <div class=\"container-IpPqBD\">\n      <form action=\"/api/v1/free?nojs=true\" method=\"post\" novalidate class=\"form form-M5sC90\"></form>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Gary Marcus 认为 Anthropic 对 Claude Mythos 的发布存在过度炒作，并指出了其测试环境简化、开源模型性能相当以及基准测试仅为渐进式提升等问题。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Gary Marcus 认为 Anthropic 对 Claude Mythos 的发布存在过度炒作，并指出了其测试环境简化、开源模型性能相当以及基准测试仅为渐进式提升等问题。",
  "summary": "在这篇评论中，Gary Marcus 剖析了围绕 Anthropic “Mythos” 模型发布的炒作。他提出了三个主要的反对观点：首先，网络安全演示（如 Firefox 漏洞利用）是在禁用了沙盒的模拟环境中进行的，这使其更像是概念验证而非即时的现实威胁。其次，他指出，当给定隔离代码时，更小、更便宜的开源权重模型也可以复制大部分相同的漏洞分析。最后，他指出 Mythos 在有效计算指数（ECI）上的表现代表了遵循现有趋势的渐进式改进，而非突破性的加速。Marcus 总结道，虽然此次发布凸显了加强监管的必要性，但媒体叙事夸大了其带来的即时危险。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Mythos 展示的网络安全威胁因简化的测试条件而被夸大了。",
      "explanation": "Firefox 漏洞利用演示依赖于先前模型的研究，并且是在关闭沙盒的情况下执行的，这并不能反映现实世界中的安全障碍。"
    },
    {
      "point": "开源权重模型可以在漏洞分析中取得类似的结果。",
      "explanation": "测试表明，当漏洞被隔离时，小型且具有成本效益的开源模型可以恢复大部分相同的分析结果，这表明 Mythos 在这方面并非具有独特的能力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Mythos 代表的是渐进式进步，而非计算效率方面的范式转移。",
      "explanation": "当根据 Epoch AI 的 ECI 等行业指标进行归一化处理时，Mythos 遵循了既定的趋势线，仅略高于 GPT-5.4，并未显示出突破性的加速。"
    }
